Title: Streetwear- global fashion movement
Festivals: ['International Film Festival Rotterdam 2022', 'Clermont-Ferrand International Short Film Festival']
Narrative:
Streetwear seems to have become a wardrobe must-have almost overnight. It definitely is one of the hottest terms in fashion today and everyone seems to have their own definition of what it is.
There are also fashion folk who appreciate the silhouettes and designs of streetwear and participate in global trends. Streetwear has since gone on to include hip-hop, sneaker culture, Japanese fashion and continue to expand its influence amd inspiration.
